            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> chopped potatoes </strong>and<strong> carrots </strong>to one side of a baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for an initial 10-15 min or until everything is starting to soften</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4? Use 2 trays!</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
