    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the root vegetables have softened, remove the tray from the oven and add the <strong>basa fillets</strong> to the other side of the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></p><p>Top the <strong>basa fillets</strong> with the <strong>cheesy breadcrumbs</strong> – this is your <strong>cheesy crusted basa</strong></p><p>Return the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> to the oven for a further 12-15 min or until the fish is cooked through and everything's golden</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked when it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
