    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the fish is cooking, boil half a kettle</p><p>Add the <strong>sugar snap peas </strong>to a pot, cover them with <strong>boiling water</strong> (just enough to cover them), add a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 3-4 min or until they're tender</p><p>Once tender, drain and return to the pot</p>",
