      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>cheesy crusted basa</strong> with the <strong>root</strong> <strong>vegetable chips</strong>,<strong> sugar snap peas</strong> and <strong>bangin' ketchup</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
